HD-HuB KPI Statistics

2018-10-25

This page collates the number of downloads and user questions for Bioconductor tools supported by the Heidelberg Centre for Human Bioinformatics as part of the German Network for Bioinformatics Infrastructure.

You can view the code used to generate these plots at https://github.com/grimbough/denbi_reporting

Plots

Number of downloads

Here we show the number of downloads from unique IP addresses each month.

Number of support questions

Support questions are made in a variety of locations. Here we track the annual number of posts tagged with the name of our tools at the Bioconductor Support Site and Biostars. We also track the number of issues opened on any Github repositories associated with each tool.
